Invocation Name: fairy tale origins
des: Today's movies got the ideas of some of its most well know and loved fairy tales from stories created long ago, but who are these authors, what details did the current movies leave out from the old tales? All the answers are here waiting. Let the true tales shine through old folklore, myths and legends that lived before the fairy tales we know today.
